#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga"
msgstr "1. One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Kimilasutta → kimbilasuttaṃ (bj) | kimbila (pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Kimilasutta"
msgstr "10. With Kimbila"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. VAR: kimilāyaṃ → kimbilāyaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.10:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kimilāyaṃ viharati veḷuvane."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kimbilā in the Freshwater Mangrove "
"Wood."

msgctxt "sn54.10:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ kimilaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Kimbila:"

msgctxt "sn54.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ bhāvito nu kho, kimila, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato "
"mahapphalo hoti mahānisaṃso”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Kimbila, how is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and "
"cultivated so that it is very fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā kimilo tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "When he said this, Kimbila kept silent."

msgctxt "sn54.10:2.2"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "For a second time …"

msgctxt "sn54.10:2.3"
msgid "tatiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ kimilaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "And for a third time, the Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn54.10:2.4"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ bhāvito nu kho, kimila, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato "
"mahapphalo hoti mahānisaṃso”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“How is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated "
"so that it is very fruitful and beneficial?”"

msgctxt "sn54.10:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho āyasmā kimilo tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "And a second time and a third time Kimbila kept silent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.323"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Ānanda said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn54.10:3.2"
msgid "“etassa, bhagavā, kālo; etassa, sugata, kālo."
msgstr "“Now is the time, Blessed One! Now is the time, Holy One!"

msgctxt "sn54.10:3.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ bhagavā ānāpānassatisamādhiṃ bhāseyya, bhagavato sutvā bhikkhū "
"dhāressantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Let the Buddha speak on immersion due to mindfulness of breathing. The "
"mendicants will listen and remember it.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:4.1"
msgid "“Tenahānanda, suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, Ānanda, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.2"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā ānando bhagavato paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Ānanda replied."

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.3"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.4"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ bhāvito ca, ānanda, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato mahapphalo "
"hoti mahānisaṃso?"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, how is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and "
"cultivated so that it is very fruitful and beneficial?"

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.5"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā nisīdati "
"pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut, sits down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establishes mindfulness right there."

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.6"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati … pe …"
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out. …"

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.7"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:4.8"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvito kho, ānanda, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato mahapphalo "
"hoti mahānisaṃso."
msgstr ""
"That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing, when developed and "
"cultivated, is very fruitful and beneficial."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti "
"pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant is breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in "
"heavily.’ When breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.2"
msgid ""
"rassaṃ vā assasanto ‘rassaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā passasanto ‘"
"rassaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When breathing in lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing in lightly.’ When "
"breathing out lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing out lightly.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.3"
msgid ""
"‘sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing the whole body.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing the whole body.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling the physical process.’ "
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling the physical process.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.5"
msgid ""
"kāye kāyānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of the body—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.7"
msgid "Kāyaññatarāhaṃ, ānanda, etaṃ vadāmi yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsaṃ."
msgstr "Because the breath is a certain aspect of the body, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.10:5.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, kāye kāyānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.324"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu ‘pītippaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"pītippaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"experiencing rapture.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out "
"experiencing rapture.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘sukhappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sukhappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’"
"ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing bliss.’ They practice "
"like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing bliss.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing the mental processes.’"
" They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing the mental "
"processes.’"

# The “inbreathing” phrase is absent from MS, however it is found in PTS.
msgctxt "sn54.10:6.4"
msgid "‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling the mental processes.’ "
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling the mental processes.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:6.5"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of feelings—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.10:6.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

#. VAR: assāsapassāsānaṃ → assāsapassāsaṃ (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn54.10:6.7"
msgid ""
"Vedanāññatarāhaṃ, ānanda, etaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsānaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"manasikāraṃ."
msgstr ""
"Because close focus on the breath is a certain aspect of feelings, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.10:6.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, vedanāsu vedanānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of feelings—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu ‘cittappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"cittappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"experiencing the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out "
"experiencing the mind.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.2"
msgid "abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in gladdening the mind.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out gladdening the mind.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.3"
msgid "samādahaṃ cittaṃ …"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in immersing the mind in samādhi.’ "
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out immersing the mind in samādhi.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.4"
msgid ""
"‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in freeing the mind.’ They practice "
"like this: ‘I’ll breathe out freeing the mind.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.5"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of the mind—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.7"
msgid ""
"Nāhaṃ, ānanda, muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa ānāpānassatisamādhibhāvanaṃ "
"vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"Because there is no development of immersion due to mindfulness of breathing "
"for someone who is unmindful and lacks awareness, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.10:7.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, citte cittānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of the mind—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu ‘aniccānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"observing impermanence.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out "
"observing impermanence.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.2"
msgid "virāgānupassī …"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing fading away.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing fading away.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.3"
msgid "nirodhānupassī …"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing cessation.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing cessation.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.6"
msgid ""
"So yaṃ taṃ hoti abhijjhādomanassānaṃ pahānaṃ taṃ paññāya disvā sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"Having seen with wisdom the giving up of desire and aversion, they watch "
"closely over with equanimity."

msgctxt "sn54.10:8.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, dhammesu dhammānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.325"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
#. VAR: catumahāpathe → cātummahāpathe (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn54.10:9.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, ānanda, catumahāpathe mahāpaṃsupuñjo."
msgstr "Suppose there was a large heap of sand at the crossroads."

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.2"
msgid ""
"Puratthimāya cepi disāyaṃ āgaccheyya sakaṭaṃ vā ratho vā, upahanateva taṃ "
"paṃsupuñjaṃ;"
msgstr "And a cart or chariot were to come by from the east,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.3"
msgid "pacchimāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya …"
msgstr "west,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.4"
msgid "uttarāya cepi disāya …"
msgstr "north,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.5"
msgid ""
"dakkhiṇāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya sakaṭaṃ vā ratho vā, upahanateva taṃ "
"paṃsupuñjaṃ."
msgstr "or south and destroy that heap of sand."

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.6"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, ānanda, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharantopi upahanateva pāpake "
"akusale dhamme;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"the body,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.7"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "feelings,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.8"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind,"

msgctxt "sn54.10:9.9"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharantopi upahanateva pāpake akusale dhamme”ti."
msgstr "or principles, they destroy bad, unskillful qualities.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.10:9.10"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.10:9.11"
msgid "Ekadhammavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.10:10.1"
msgid "Ekadhammo ca bojjhaṅgo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.10:10.2"
msgid "suddhikañca duve phalā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.10:10.3"
msgid "Ariṭṭho kappino dīpo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.10:10.4"
msgid "vesālī kimilena cāti."
msgstr ""
